gui

Class ComponentGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.ComponentGenerator

  • public class ComponentGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing public static methods used to generate various graphical components. Also defines public static Font and Color instance fields for use throughout the GUI.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Jacob Jones, Andrew Rottier
